hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 有效势的极值满足
$$\frac{dV_{eff}}{d\phi}=0\;\Longrightarrow\;\Bigl(\frac{\rho_e}{M^2}-\mu^2\Bigr)\phi+\lambda\phi^3=0.$$
对于 $\rho_e<\mu^2M^2$，非零 VEV 为
$$\phi_e=\sqrt{\frac{\mu^2-\rho_e/M^2}{\lambda}}\,. $$

2. 在高密度物体（$\rho_c>\mu^2M^2$）内部，场被恢复，其质量为
$$m_c^2=\frac{\rho_c}{M^2}-\mu^2,\qquad m_c=\sqrt{\frac{\rho_c}{M^2}-\mu^2}\,. $$

3. 薄壳-厚壳转变发生在
$$\chi_e=\frac{\phi_e}{m_cR_c}=1\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\sqrt{\frac{\mu^2-\rho_{crit}/M^2}{\lambda}}
=R_c\sqrt{\frac{\rho_c}{M^2}-\mu^2}\,. $$

4. 将两边平方并求解 $\rho_{crit}$：
$$\frac{\mu^2-\rho_{crit}/M^2}{\lambda}
=R_c^2\Bigl(\frac{\rho_c}{M^2}-\mu^2\Bigr)
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\mu^2-\frac{\rho_{crit}}{M^2}
=\lambda R_c^2\Bigl(\frac{\rho_c}{M^2}-\mu^2\Bigr)$$
$$\frac{\rho_{crit}}{M^2}
=\mu^2-\lambda R_c^2\Bigl(\frac{\rho_c}{M^2}-\mu^2\Bigr)
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\rho_{crit}
=M^2\mu^2-\lambda R_c^2\bigl(\rho_c-\mu^2M^2\bigr)\,. $$
